OL,3,C'Revolutionary' skin sensor could
OL,4,Cchange how eczema is treated
OL,6,FIt is hoped the "groundbreaking"
OL,7,Fdevice will help improve treatment
OL,8,Foptions for people with eczema, as STV
OL,9,FReporter Amie Flett reports.
OL,11,FFor years, people living with eczema
OL,12,Fhave endured endless trial-and-error
OL,13,Ftreatments and long waiting lists to
OL,14,Fsee a dermatologist.
OL,16,FNow scientists at Heriot-Watt
OL,17,FUniversity in Edinburgh believe
OL,18,Fthey've developed groundbreaking
OL,19,Ftechnology that could revolutionise
OL,20,Fhow the condition is diagnosed and
OL,21,Ftreated.
