OL,3,C'Revolutionary' skin sensor could
OL,4,Cchange how eczema is treated
OL,6,FThe device is a sensor that measures
OL,7,Fmaterial changes in each layer of skin
OL,8,Fusing small vibrations on the surface
OL,9,Fto detect changes in tissue stiffness
OL,10,Fand fluid.
OL,12,FThe aim is to have the tool available
OL,13,Fin local pharmacies across the UK,
OL,14,Feasing pressure on the NHS and
OL,15,Fcreating simpler pathways to care.
