OL,3,C'Revolutionary' skin sensor could
OL,4,Cchange how eczema is treated
OL,6,FProfessor Michael Crichton, who is
OL,7,Fbased in the school of engineering and
OL,8,Fphysical sciences, said the technology
OL,9,F"represents a fundamental shift in how
OL,10,Fwe approach eczema management".
OL,12,FHe added: "Rather than relying solely
OL,13,Fon visual assessments, which haven't
OL,14,Fevolved in decades and can be
OL,15,Fparticularly unreliable for patients
OL,16,Fwith darker skin tones, our sensor
OL,17,Fprovides objective measurements of
OL,18,Fwhat's happening beneath the skin's
OL,19,Fsurface."
