OL,3,C'Revolutionary' skin sensor could
OL,4,Cchange how eczema is treated
OL,6,FThey will also gather feedback from
OL,7,Fpatients and clinicians on its
OL,8,Fusability.
OL,10,FProfessor Richard Weller, dermatology
OL,11,Flead for NHS Research Scotland and a
OL,12,FUniversity of Edinburgh academic based
OL,13,Fat the Institute for Regeneration and
OL,14,FRepair, explained: "The current system
OL,15,Ffor managing eczema is outdated and
OL,16,Finefficient.
